KOUSUKE gasp]

00:53:42.168 --> 00:53:43.369 position:19% line:89% align:start
Where'd you come from?

00:53:43.402 --> 00:53:46.272 position:5% line:83% align:start
Didn't you just head off to the
baseball field a second ago?

00:53:46.305 --> 00:53:47.306 position:27% line:89% align:start
Never mind that!

00:53:47.340 --> 00:53:49.476 position:13% line:83% align:start
This girl here was saying
that her grandmother

00:53:49.509 --> 00:53:51.177 position:19% line:83% align:start
was so grateful about
you coming around

00:53:51.210 --> 00:53:53.447 position:19% line:83% align:start
and taking care of her
at her retirement home.

00:53:53.480 --> 00:53:55.582 position:30% line:83% align:start
I'm impressed,
Kousuke! So anyway...

00:53:55.615 --> 00:53:58.918 position:7% line:83% align:start
Uh... How do you know all that
stuff about my grandmother?!

00:53:58.951 --> 00:54:02.154 position:19% line:83% align:start
Who, me? Uh, I met her
at the bowling alley...

00:54:02.188 --> 00:54:03.590 position:5% line:89% align:start
But my grandmother's bedridden!

00:54:03.623 --> 00:54:05.325 position:38% line:83% align:start
[MAKOTO]
Oh! Um, my mistake.

00:54:05.359 --> 00:54:07.260 position:27% line:83% align:start
Let me know when
you're done gabbing.

00:54:07.294 --> 00:54:11.431 position:7% line:83% align:start
--[KAHO, MORIKO, SEKIMI] Uh...
--No, hang on, Kousuke!

00:54:11.465 --> 00:54:14.134 position:38% line:89% align:start
[groans]

00:54:14.167 --> 00:54:16.035 position:27% line:89% align:start
[MAKOTO panting]

00:54:16.068 --> 00:54:17.404 position:38% line:83% align:start
[MAKOTO]
One more time!

00:54:18.672 --> 00:54:20.940 position:44% line:89% align:start
Ha!

00:54:23.510 --> 00:54:26.079 position:24% line:89% align:start
[MAKOTO groaning]

00:54:26.113 --> 00:54:28.548 position:30% line:89% align:start
Um... Well...

00:54:28.582 --> 00:54:30.984 position:38% line:83% align:start
[MAKOTO]
Kousuke!

00:54:31.017 --> 00:54:31.918 position:38% line:89% align:start
Uh-huh?

00:54:31.952 --> 00:54:32.786 position:38% line:83% align:start
[MAKOTO]
Hold on...

00:54:32.819 --> 00:54:33.920 position:19% line:83% align:start
[KAHO, MORIKO, SEKIMI,
KOUSUKE gasp]

00:54:33.954 --> 00:54:35.989 position:19% line:83% align:start
Where'd you come from?
Didn't you just head off to--

00:54:36.022 --> 00:54:36.656 position:38% line:89% align:start
Hold it!

00:54:36.690 --> 00:54:37.557 position:10% line:89% align:start
You're being such a coward!

00:54:37.591 --> 00:54:39.159 position:21% line:83% align:start
What's the point of
getting all sulky

00:54:39.192 --> 00:54:40.394 position:30% line:83% align:start
