got a better mark?

00:54:40.427 --> 00:54:42.462 position:27% line:83% align:start
This has nothing
to do with that!

00:54:42.496 --> 00:54:44.498 position:10% line:83% align:start
What's your problem, showin'
up braggin' your head off?!

00:54:44.531 --> 00:54:46.233 position:21% line:83% align:start
And what has nothing
to do with what?!

00:54:46.266 --> 00:54:49.369 position:5% line:83% align:start
I'm saying that the test scores
and the fact that Kaho's in love

00:54:49.403 --> 00:54:51.405 position:19% line:83% align:start
with you, have nothing
to do with eachother.

00:54:51.438 --> 00:54:52.439 position:30% line:89% align:start
It's not true!

00:54:52.472 --> 00:54:53.173 position:38% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:54:53.206 --> 00:54:54.574 position:30% line:89% align:start
It's not true!

00:54:54.608 --> 00:54:56.510 position:38% line:83% align:start
[MAKOTO]
Ah... Wait! Kaho!

00:54:56.543 --> 00:54:58.211 position:27% line:83% align:start
Well, you heard
what the girl said.

00:54:58.245 --> 00:55:00.480 position:19% line:89% align:start
Uh! Don't go, Kousuke!

00:55:00.514 --> 00:55:03.216 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:55:03.250 --> 00:55:05.118 position:38% line:89% align:start
[groans]

00:55:05.152 --> 00:55:08.388 position:27% line:89% align:start
[MAKOTO panting]

00:55:08.422 --> 00:55:11.492 position:16% line:83% align:start
[MAKOTO] I've gotta take
a simpler approach to this.

00:55:11.526 --> 00:55:13.561 position:35% line:89% align:start
[screams]

00:55:13.594 --> 00:55:16.296 position:35% line:83% align:start
[SWIMMERS]
Ohh...

00:55:18.031 --> 00:55:20.435 position:27% line:89% align:start
[MAKOTO screams]

00:55:20.468 --> 00:55:24.004 position:27% line:89% align:start
[grunts, groans]

00:55:24.037 --> 00:55:25.172 position:38% line:83% align:start
[MIYUKI]
What's with all the commotion?

00:55:25.205 --> 00:55:27.341 position:5% line:89% align:start
