00:55:38.319 --> 00:55:39.654 position:35% line:83% align:start
[KOUSUKE]
Hm?

00:55:42.123 --> 00:55:43.591 position:38% line:83% align:start
[MAKOTO]
Mm... Hm?

00:55:43.624 --> 00:55:44.725 position:30% line:89% align:start
Unbelievable.

00:55:44.759 --> 00:55:46.727 position:16% line:89% align:start
[STUDENT C, D grunting]

00:55:46.761 --> 00:55:49.230 position:33% line:83% align:start
[STUDENT C]
Now for the headlock!

00:55:49.263 --> 00:55:50.631 position:38% line:83% align:start
[MAKOTO]
Ha!

00:55:50.665 --> 00:55:52.333 position:33% line:83% align:start
[STUDENT C]
Huh? What was that?

00:55:52.366 --> 00:55:53.234 position:33% line:83% align:start
[STUDENT D]
Amazing...

00:55:53.267 --> 00:55:55.369 position:10% line:89% align:start
Quit staring. Just carry on!

00:55:55.403 --> 00:55:57.271 position:27% line:83% align:start
Could you move?
I need this spot.

00:55:57.305 --> 00:55:58.506 position:27% line:83% align:start
[FEMALE STUDENT]
Kaho!

00:55:58.539 --> 00:55:59.540 position:41% line:83% align:start
[KAHO]
Huh?

00:55:59.574 --> 00:56:00.641 position:13% line:89% align:start
I don't exactly know why,

00:56:00.675 --> 00:56:03.077 position:16% line:83% align:start
but someone wants you to
come down to the courtyard.

00:56:03.110 --> 00:56:04.645 position:35% line:89% align:start
Who does?

00:56:04.679 --> 00:56:06.180 position:35% line:83% align:start
[KOUSUKE]
Tell me where we're going!

00:56:06.214 --> 00:56:07.215 position:7% line:89% align:start
What're you gonna make me do?

00:56:07.248 --> 00:56:08.616 position:7% line:89% align:start
You'll know when we get there!

00:56:08.649 --> 00:56:10.017 position:41% line:83% align:start
[YURI]
Makoto?

00:56:10.051 --> 00:56:11.085 position:38% line:83% align:start
[MAKOTO]
Later!

00:56:11.118 --> 00:56:13.054 position:16% line:89% align:start
Okay! Okay! You got me!

00:56:13.087 --> 00:56:15.289 position:19% line:83% align:start
You think this is what
she meant by the courtyard?

00:56:15.323 --> 00:56:16.692 position:35% line:89% align:start
Who knows?

00:56:16.725 --> 00:56:19.227 position:19% line:83% align:start
--[STUDENT C laughing]
