00:56:19.260 --> 00:56:22.029 position:27% line:89% align:start
Stand... there.

00:56:22.831 --> 00:56:23.431 position:33% line:83% align:start
[STUDENT C]
Ah!

00:56:23.464 --> 00:56:25.399 position:13% line:89% align:start
[STUDENT D, KOUSUKE grunt]

00:56:27.268 --> 00:56:28.804 position:7% line:89% align:start
[STUDENT D, KOUSUKE groaning]

00:56:28.837 --> 00:56:32.206 position:21% line:83% align:start
