00:56:45.821 --> 00:56:47.456 position:10% line:89% align:start
Kousuke, what are you doing?

00:56:47.489 --> 00:56:49.090 position:16% line:89% align:start
Put your arm around me.

00:56:49.123 --> 00:56:51.260 position:27% line:89% align:start
Uh... Thank you.

00:56:51.293 --> 00:56:53.362 position:21% line:83% align:start
