something beautiful!

00:56:57.533 --> 00:56:59.535 position:35% line:89% align:start
All right!

00:56:59.568 --> 00:57:02.437 position:16% line:83% align:start
Everything's good again,
thanks to yours truly.

00:57:02.471 --> 00:57:04.706 position:13% line:83% align:start
I can't remember the last
time I felt so happy!

00:57:04.740 --> 00:57:07.609 position:35% line:83% align:start
[giggles]
Huh?!

00:57:07.643 --> 00:57:09.378 position:30% line:89% align:start
It's changed!

00:57:09.411 --> 00:57:12.347 position:19% line:89% align:start
Ten? What's that mean?

00:57:12.381 --> 00:57:14.082 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:57:14.116 --> 00:57:15.617 position:41% line:89% align:start
Mm...

00:57:15.651 --> 00:57:18.120 position:44% line:89% align:start
One?

00:57:18.153 --> 00:57:27.095 position:30% line:89% align:start
[piano plays]

00:58:17.714 --> 00:58:22.819 position:13% line:83% align:start
[MAKOTO] Not here. Maybe I
got here a little too early.

00:58:22.852 --> 00:58:25.388 position:41% line:89% align:start
Huh?!

00:58:30.326 --> 00:58:32.829 position:38% line:83% align:start
[MAKOTO]
There he is...

00:58:45.876 --> 00:58:49.512 position:30% line:83% align:start
Um, excuse me!
I have a question for yo...

00:58:49.545 --> 00:58:53.249 position:35% line:89% align:start
Huh? Yuri!

00:58:53.282 --> 00:58:55.318 position:7% line:89% align:start
You scared the life outta me!

00:58:55.351 --> 00:58:56.719 position:38% line:83% align:start
[MAKOTO]
How come you're here?

00:58:56.754 --> 00:58:58.588 position:21% line:83% align:start
[YURI] I brought the
notebooks up for you.

00:58:58.621 --> 00:59:02.291 position:21% line:83% align:start
You forgot you're on
duty today, I bet.

00:59:02.325 --> 00:59:03.626 position:35% line:89% align:start
Oh! Right!

00:59:03.661 --> 00:59:05.528 position:30% line:83% align:start
[YURI laughs]
I figured as much.

00:59:05.561 --> 00:59:07.931 position:19% line:83% align:start
I hope you appreciate
our friendship here.

00:59:07.965 --> 00:59:09.933 position:13% line:89% align:start
So, what's your question?

00:59:09.967 --> 00:59:11.835 position:10% line:89% align:start
Oh, uh, nothing! Forget it!

00:59:11.869 --> 00:59:13.403 position:41% line:83% align:start
[YURI]
Okay.

00:59:17.541 --> 00:59:18.609 position:35% line:89% align:start
Hey, Yuri!

00:59:18.642 --> 00:59:19.510 position:41% line:83% align:start
[YURI]
Yeah?

00:59:19.543 --> 00:59:21.979 position:24% line:83% align:start
Did you see anyone
on your way up here?

00:59:22.012 --> 00:59:23.279 position:41% line:83% align:start
[YURI]
Like who?

00:59:23.312 --> 00:59:25.248 position:38% line:83% align:start
[MAKOTO]
Uh, never mind.

00:59:25.281 --> 00:59:26.617 position:41% line:83% align:start
[YURI]
All right.

00:59:28.886 --> 00:59:32.489 position:27% line:89% align:start
[phone vibrates]

00:59:32.523 --> 00:59:33.957 position:38% line:83% align:start
[MAKOTO]
It's from Kousuke...

00:59:33.991 --> 00:59:36.960 position:16% line:83% align:start
"She just asked me out.
Jealous?"

00:59:36.994 --> 00:59:39.296 position:33% line:89% align:start
Heh. Whater.

00:59:39.329 --> 00:59:42.700 position:13% line:83% align:start
Who do ya think set it up
for you in the first place?

00:59:42.733 --> 00:59:44.268 position:38% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:59:48.272 --> 00:59:49.540 position:35% line:89% align:start
Oh, no...

00:59:51.375 --> 00:59:52.710 position:35% line:83% align:start
[KOUSUKE]
Ma...

00:59:52.743 --> 00:59:53.877 position:41% line:89% align:start
Ko...

00:59:53.911 --> 00:59:56.280 position:33% line:89% align:start
To... There.

00:59:56.313 --> 00:59:57.347 position:24% line:89% align:start
Where do you live?

00:59:57.381 --> 00:59:59.450 position:13% line:83% align:start
[KAHO] On the south side,
right past the station.

00:59:59.483 --> 01:00:01.819 position:13% line:83% align:start
[KOUSUKE] We should get my
dad to check out your ankle.

01:00:01.852 --> 01:00:02.753 position:41% line:83% align:start
[KAHO]
Uh?

01:00:02.786 --> 01:00:04.421 position:35% line:83% align:start
[KOUSUKE]
Our clinic isn't far from here.

01:00:04.455 --> 01:00:05.156 position:35% line:89% align:start
[panting]

01:00:05.190 --> 01:00:07.658 position:41% line:83% align:start
[YURI]
Come to think of it...

01:00:07.691 --> 01:00:12.730 position:10% line:83% align:start
I did actually pass someone
on my way up here!

01:00:12.763 --> 01:00:15.265 position:30% line:89% align:start
It was Chiaki.

01:00:15.299 --> 01:00:18.335 position:35% line:89% align:start
[panting]

01:00:18.368 --> 01:00:19.470 position:38% line:89% align:start
Kousuke!

01:00:19.503 --> 01:00:20.671 position:33% line:83% align:start
[STUDENT K]
He went home.

01:00:20.704 --> 01:00:22.974 position:5% line:83% align:start
[STUDENT L] Yeah, holding hands
with that first year girl.

01:00:23.007 --> 01:00:24.709 position:19% line:89% align:start
[STUDENT K, L chuckle]

01:00:26.477 --> 01:00:28.646 position:38% line:83% align:start
[MAKOTO]
It's gone...

01:00:33.785 --> 01:00:34.986 position:24% line:89% align:start
Answer the phone.

01:00:35.019 --> 01:00:38.455 position:7% line:83% align:start
Yeah, it's me, Dad. I've, uh,
got a sprain ankle for you.

01:00:38.489 --> 01:00:40.324 position:21% line:83% align:start
Think maybe you can
take a look at it?

01:00:40.357 --> 01:00:42.527 position:27% line:89% align:start
No, it's not me.

01:00:42.560 --> 01:00:44.596 position:24% line:83% align:start
Yeah, sure, we'll
be right there.

01:00:44.629 --> 01:00:45.964 position:41% line:83% align:start
[KAHO]
Thanks for all this.

01:00:45.997 --> 01:00:48.566 position:13% line:83% align:start
[VOICEMAIL] Please leave a
message after the beep.

01:00:48.600 --> 01:00:50.300 position:41% line:89% align:start
Damn!

01:00:50.334 --> 01:00:51.402 position:27% line:89% align:start
[whistle blows]

01:00:51.436 --> 01:00:54.672 position:27% line:89% align:start
[MAKOTO panting]

01:01:01.546 --> 01:01:04.315 position:24% line:83% align:start
[MAKOTO] What now?
Should I go back in time?

01:01:04.349 --> 01:01:07.552 position:13% line:83% align:start
Then again, it's not like
anything's happened yet.

01:01:09.954 --> 01:01:11.923 position:16% line:89% align:start
[crossing gates ringing]

01:01:11.956 --> 01:01:14.058 position:27% line:89% align:start
[MAKOTO panting]

01:01:14.093 --> 01:01:16.027 position:16% line:89% align:start
[crossing gates ringing]

01:01:16.060 --> 01:01:17.796 position:27% line:89% align:start
[MAKOTO panting]

01:01:17.829 --> 01:01:21.033 position:21% line:89% align:start
[train horn blares]

01:01:21.066 --> 01:01:23.935 position:27% line:89% align:start
[MAKOTO panting]

01:02:00.973 --> 01:02:02.575 position:30% line:89% align:start
Uh, 'scuse me!

01:02:02.608 --> 01:02:05.110 position:13% line:83% align:start
You wouldn't know if there
was a bike accident here?

01:02:05.144 --> 01:02:08.681 position:35% line:83% align:start
[WOMAN C]
Uh... No. I-I don't think so.

01:02:08.714 --> 01:02:10.416 position:38% line:83% align:start
[MAKOTO]
Okay. Thanks.

01:02:10.449 --> 01:02:13.052 position:19% line:83% align:start
[WOMAN C] An accident,
she said. How scary.

01:02:14.987 --> 01:02:17.489 position:27% line:89% align:start
[phone vibrates]

01:02:17.523 --> 01:02:21.927 position:5% line:89% align:start
Kousuke? Where are you? Kousuke?

01:02:21.961 --> 01:02:23.662 position:38% line:89% align:start
Huh...?

01:02:26.498 --> 01:02:27.833 position:38% line:83% align:start
[MAKOTO]
Chiaki.

01:02:30.469 --> 01:02:32.004 position:38% line:83% align:start
[CHIAKI]
Kousuke's over at his place.

01:02:32.037 --> 01:02:33.173 position:13% line:89% align:start
Hey, uh, what's the deal?!

01:02:33.206 --> 01:02:34.840 position:21% line:83% align:start
You guys didn't show
up at the field!

01:02:34.874 --> 01:02:36.809 position:24% line:83% align:start
--[MAKOTO] Sorry.
--[CHIAKI] I'm still waiting.

01:02:36.842 --> 01:02:38.711 position:30% line:83% align:start
--Wait a sec!
--Yeah?

01:02:38.744 --> 01:02:40.880 position:38% line:83% align:start
[MAKOTO]
Chiaki, there's something

01:02:40.913 --> 01:02:44.050 position:16% line:83% align:start
I've been wanting to ask
you for a while now.

01:02:44.084 --> 01:02:46.852 position:27% line:83% align:start
Do you have fun
playing ball with me?

01:02:46.886 --> 01:02:48.021 position:38% line:83% align:start
[CHIAKI]
What're you talking about?

01:02:48.054 --> 01:02:50.589 position:10% line:83% align:start
I mean, I have a lot of fun
playing baseball with you.

01:02:50.623 --> 01:02:52.058 position:24% line:83% align:start
[CHIAKI chuckles]
You sure suck

01:02:52.092 --> 01:02:53.525 position:27% line:83% align:start
for someone who
likes it so much.

01:02:53.559 --> 01:02:55.195 position:27% line:83% align:start
You'd suck too,
if enthusiasm didn't count.

01:02:55.228 --> 01:02:57.429 position:24% line:83% align:start
[CHIAKI chuckles]
That's better than nothing.

01:02:57.463 --> 01:02:59.833 position:38% line:89% align:start
[laughs]

01:02:59.866 --> 01:03:02.568 position:38% line:83% align:start
[CHIAKI]
What's so funny?

01:03:02.601 --> 01:03:05.839 position:16% line:83% align:start
It's nice talkin' to ya.
It feels like it's been ages.

01:03:05.872 --> 01:03:06.806 position:38% line:83% align:start
[CHIAKI]
What're you talking about?

01:03:06.840 --> 01:03:08.507 position:10% line:89% align:start
We've been talking all day.

01:03:08.540 --> 01:03:10.643 position:13% line:89% align:start
Oh, right. Yeah. I guess.

01:03:10.676 --> 01:03:12.078 position:38% line:83% align:start
[CHIAKI]
You miss me that much, huh?

01:03:12.112 --> 01:03:13.612 position:38% line:83% align:start
[MAKOTO]
Ah! Don't be so stupid!

01:03:13.646 --> 01:03:18.184 position:38% line:83% align:start
[CHIAKI]
I'm kidding! Kidding! Calm down.

01:03:18.218 --> 01:03:19.451 position:24% line:89% align:start
Actually, Makoto,

01:03:19.485 --> 01:03:22.722 position:7% line:83% align:start
[sighs] there's something I've
been meaning to ask you as well.

01:03:22.756 --> 01:03:23.890 position:38% line:83% align:start
[MAKOTO]
Oh, yeah?

01:03:23.924 --> 01:03:25.659 position:10% line:83% align:start
[CHIAKI] You're gonna think
this is seriously whacked.

01:03:25.692 --> 01:03:28.460 position:38% line:83% align:start
[MAKOTO]
So, what is it?

01:03:28.495 --> 01:03:32.065 position:24% line:83% align:start
--[CHIAKI] Well...
--[MAKOTO] Come on. Spit it out.

01:03:32.098 --> 01:03:34.668 position:38% line:83% align:start
[CHIAKI]
Have you been...

01:03:34.701 --> 01:03:36.436 position:27% line:89% align:start
...time leaping?

01:03:41.775 --> 01:03:44.077 position:21% line:83% align:start
[CHIAKI] You've been
time leaping, right?

01:03:45.745 --> 01:03:47.681 position:38% line:83% align:start
[CHIAKI]
Hey, Makoto...

01:03:47.714 --> 01:03:48.615 position:38% line:83% align:start
[MAKOTO]
Huh. Uh...

01:03:48.648 --> 01:03:49.783 position:38% line:83% align:start
[CHIAKI]
Makoto!

01:03:53.853 --> 01:03:57.023 position:13% line:83% align:start
[CHIAKI] Actually, Makoto,
there's something

01:03:57.057 --> 01:03:58.925 position:24% line:83% align:start
I've been meaning
to ask you as well.

01:03:58.959 --> 01:04:03.064 position:16% line:83% align:start
You're gonna think this
is seriously whacked. Well...

01:04:03.097 --> 01:04:03.897 position:38% line:83% align:start
[MAKOTO]
No wait!

01:04:03.930 --> 01:04:04.864 position:21% line:83% align:start
--Hang on a second!
--[CHIAKI] Uh...

01:04:04.898 --> 01:04:06.267 position:21% line:83% align:start
[MAKOTO] Let's talk
about my little sister.

01:04:06.300 --> 01:04:07.335 position:38% line:83% align:start
[CHIAKI]
Huh? Why?

01:04:07.368 --> 01:04:10.137 position:16% line:83% align:start
[MAKOTO] 'Cause. Oh man,
is my sister ever stupid--

01:04:10.171 --> 01:04:12.906 position:38% line:83% align:start
[CHIAKI]
Uh. Hello, I was talking here.

01:04:12.939 --> 01:04:17.644 position:16% line:83% align:start
Uh... U-Uh. Never mind.
I'll be waitin' here for ya.

01:04:19.947 --> 01:04:23.516 position:7% line:89% align:start
How does Chiaki know about it?

01:04:23.550 --> 01:04:25.920 position:38% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

01:04:25.953 --> 01:04:28.823 position:16% line:83% align:start
[MAKOTO] Zero? So these
digits did represent

01:04:28.856 --> 01:04:30.992 position:21% line:83% align:start
the number of times
I could time leap.

01:04:31.025 --> 01:04:34.095 position:21% line:83% align:start
I wasted my last one
on something so lame.

01:04:34.128 --> 01:04:36.697 position:21% line:83% align:start
Oh, well. No biggie.
Kousuke wasn't hurt,

01:04:36.731 --> 01:04:37.865 position:7% line:89% align:start
and that's what really counts.

01:04:37.898 --> 01:04:39.767 position:35% line:83% align:start
[KOUSUKE]
Hey, Makoto!

01:04:39.800 --> 01:04:43.704 position:21% line:89% align:start
[bike chain whirls]

01:04:48.109 --> 01:04:49.010 position:30% line:89% align:start
[MAKOTO gasps]

01:04:49.043 --> 01:04:53.280 position:19% line:83% align:start
I need to borrow your
bike a bit longer!

01:04:53.314 --> 01:04:55.883 position:30% line:83% align:start
Wait, Kousuke!
No, stop!

01:04:55.916 --> 01:04:57.118 position:16% line:89% align:start
[WOMAN B, MAKOTO groan]

01:04:57.151 --> 01:04:58.586 position:27% line:89% align:start
[MAKOTO screams]

01:04:58.619 --> 01:04:59.653 position:35% line:83% align:start
[WOMAN B]
Honestly!

01:04:59.687 --> 01:05:03.224 position:13% line:83% align:start
Watch where you're going!
Apologize at once! Hey!

01:05:03.257 --> 01:05:04.792 position:41% line:89% align:start
Look!

01:05:08.162 --> 01:05:11.299 position:16% line:89% align:start
Stop, Kousuke! Kousuke!

01:05:12.066 --> 01:05:13.868 position:16% line:89% align:start
[crossing gate ringing]

01:05:13.901 --> 01:05:15.603 position:21% line:89% align:start
[train horn blares]

01:05:15.636 --> 01:05:17.938 position:30% line:89% align:start
Wait, Kousuke!

01:05:17.972 --> 01:05:19.307 position:41% line:89% align:start
Stop!

01:05:22.210 --> 01:05:24.346 position:24% line:89% align:start
Kousuke! Kousuke!

01:05:24.379 --> 01:05:26.148 position:35% line:89% align:start
[grunting]

01:05:26.181 --> 01:05:28.116 position:38% line:83% align:start
[MAKOTO]
Kousuke...

01:05:28.150 --> 01:05:30.118 position:38% line:89% align:start
Kousuke!

01:05:31.652 --> 01:05:35.890 position:13% line:89% align:start
[MAKOTO grunts, groaning]

01:05:41.296 --> 01:05:46.268 position:27% line:89% align:start
[CROWD murmurs]

01:05:46.301 --> 01:05:51.106 position:33% line:89% align:start
[whimpering]

01:05:51.139 --> 01:06:03.151 position:33% line:89% align:start
[bell tolls]

01:06:15.263 --> 01:06:25.674 position:13% line:83% align:start
[MAKOTO] Stop! Stop! Stop!
Stop! Stop! Stop! Stop!

01:06:25.707 --> 01:06:28.944 position:38% line:89% align:start
Stoooop!

01:06:42.958 --> 01:06:46.362 position:38% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

01:06:46.395 --> 01:06:47.929 position:38% line:83% align:start
[MAKOTO]
Huh?

01:06:49.831 --> 01:06:53.302 position:35% line:89% align:start
Huh? Huh?!

01:06:55.271 --> 01:06:57.073 position:38% line:83% align:start
[MAKOTO]
What's going on?

01:06:57.106 --> 01:06:58.840 position:38% line:83% align:start
[CHIAKI]
I knew it was you.

01:06:58.874 --> 01:07:01.077 position:30% line:89% align:start
[MAKOTO gasps]

01:07:01.110 --> 01:07:02.711 position:38% line:83% align:start
[MAKOTO]
Chiaki?!

01:07:02.744 --> 01:07:05.214 position:13% line:89% align:start
What're... you doing here?

01:07:05.248 --> 01:07:07.250 position:27% line:89% align:start
Where's Kousuke?

01:07:07.283 --> 01:07:09.051 position:16% line:89% align:start
Probably still at home.

01:07:09.085 --> 01:07:12.654 position:38% line:83% align:start
[MAKOTO]
What? But he was just here...

01:07:15.358 --> 01:07:16.893 position:38% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

01:07:19.395 --> 01:07:22.832 position:38% line:83% align:start
[MAKOTO]
Wait... Did you do this?!

01:07:22.865 --> 01:07:26.135 position:5% line:89% align:start
You can time leap too, Chiaki?!

01:07:26.169 --> 01:07:27.336 position:33% line:89% align:start
Would you...

01:07:27.370 --> 01:07:32.074 position:7% line:83% align:start
Would you laugh if I told you
I came from... the future?

01:08:32.035 --> 01:08:34.338 position:21% line:83% align:start
[CHIAKI] In my time,
a device is developed

01:08:34.371 --> 01:08:40.077 position:10% line:83% align:start
that allows people to travel
through time whenever they want.

01:08:40.110 --> 01:08:44.881 position:27% line:83% align:start
This is it here.
You use it to charge your body.

01:08:44.915 --> 01:08:48.952 position:7% line:83% align:start
That's how I came to this era,
with this device.

01:08:48.986 --> 01:08:54.057 position:7% line:83% align:start
I didn't realize it at first,
but somewhere along the way...

01:08:54.091 --> 01:08:56.460 position:30% line:89% align:start
...I lost it.

01:08:56.493 --> 01:08:59.830 position:5% line:83% align:start
I panicked. I looked everywhere
and eventually I found it.

01:08:59.863 --> 01:09:03.867 position:21% line:89% align:start
In the science lab.

01:09:03.900 --> 01:09:07.371 position:21% line:83% align:start
But by then, it was
already used up.

01:09:08.606 --> 01:09:13.844 position:5% line:83% align:start
[CHIAKI] It wasn't all bad news.
It was charged to an idiot.

01:09:13.877 --> 01:09:15.312 position:16% line:89% align:start
I had trouble sleeping,

01:09:15.346 --> 01:09:18.181 position:19% line:83% align:start
thinking it might fall
into the wrong hands.

01:09:19.850 --> 01:09:23.020 position:21% line:89% align:start
Why'd you come here?

01:09:23.053 --> 01:09:25.856 position:27% line:89% align:start
'Cause I had to.

01:09:25.889 --> 01:09:27.525 position:38% line:83% align:start
[MAKOTO]
Why though?

01:09:31.229 --> 01:09:34.898 position:7% line:83% align:start
[CHIAKI] There was a painting
I desperately wanted to see.

01:09:34.931 --> 01:09:37.235 position:7% line:89% align:start
No matter how far away it was,

01:09:37.268 --> 01:09:39.470 position:27% line:83% align:start
or what sort of
place it was in.

01:09:39.504 --> 01:09:41.838 position:13% line:89% align:start
No matter how dangerous...

01:09:44.609 --> 01:09:47.578 position:38% line:83% align:start
[CHIAKI]
...I wanted to see it.

01:09:52.383 --> 01:09:53.985 position:13% line:89% align:start
Unfortunately, in my time,

01:09:54.018 --> 01:09:55.920 position:16% line:83% align:start
the painting had already
been destroyed.

01:09:55.953 --> 01:09:59.390 position:16% line:83% align:start
And before these times,
its whereabouts was unknown.

01:09:59.424 --> 01:10:01.893 position:7% line:83% align:start
The only place where there was
an accurate record of it

01:10:01.926 --> 01:10:05.063 position:16% line:83% align:start
was in this present era,
in this place.

01:10:05.096 --> 01:10:07.398 position:10% line:89% align:start
It was here, in this season.

01:10:07.432 --> 01:10:11.402 position:5% line:89% align:start
And so you came all... this way?

01:10:11.436 --> 01:10:15.473 position:10% line:89% align:start
All I needed was to see it.

01:10:15.506 --> 01:10:19.110 position:13% line:83% align:start
I was going to remember it
for the rest of my life.

01:10:25.517 --> 01:10:29.987 position:13% line:83% align:start
[CHIAKI] Anyway... I guess
there's no point now.

01:10:30.021 --> 01:10:31.356 position:33% line:89% align:start
To anything.

01:10:33.224 --> 01:10:35.293 position:38% line:83% align:start
[MAKOTO]
Huh?

01:10:35.326 --> 01:10:38.364 position:24% line:83% align:start
You can't return?!
What's that supposed to mean?!

01:10:38.397 --> 01:10:42.334 position:10% line:83% align:start
[CHIAKI] It means just that,
I can't go back to my time.

01:10:42.368 --> 01:10:44.235 position:38% line:83% align:start
[MAKOTO]
I know, but why?!

01:10:44.269 --> 01:10:45.937 position:16% line:83% align:start
[CHIAKI] Because having
to steal your bike

01:10:45.970 --> 01:10:48.005 position:27% line:83% align:start
that Kousuke was
supposed to ride

01:10:48.039 --> 01:10:52.177 position:21% line:83% align:start
used up all the time
leaps that I had left.

01:10:52.211 --> 01:10:54.179 position:38% line:83% align:start
[gasps]
What'll you do?!

01:10:54.213 --> 01:10:56.047 position:13% line:89% align:start
There's nothing I can do.

01:10:56.080 --> 01:10:57.982 position:21% line:83% align:start
Why would you use it
up for that?!

01:10:58.015 --> 01:11:00.085 position:10% line:83% align:start
Didn't you think to save it
for when you really needed it?!

01:11:00.119 --> 01:11:02.987 position:24% line:83% align:start
I did save it for
something important.

01:11:03.020 --> 01:11:05.624 position:13% line:83% align:start
You probably haven't fully
realized it yet, Makoto,

01:11:05.657 --> 01:11:08.227 position:21% line:83% align:start
but Kousuke and that
girl did die once

01:11:08.260 --> 01:11:10.462 position:16% line:89% align:start
at that train crossing.

01:11:10.496 --> 01:11:13.665 position:7% line:83% align:start
A certain someone was sobbing
and blaming herself for it,

01:11:13.699 --> 01:11:16.602 position:24% line:83% align:start
so it was the only
choice I really had.

01:11:20.005 --> 01:11:22.274 position:38% line:83% align:start
[CHIAKI]
I was supposed to go home,

01:11:22.307 --> 01:11:26.512 position:19% line:83% align:start
but before I knew it,
summer was already here.

01:11:26.545 --> 01:11:31.216 position:7% line:83% align:start
I couldn't help it. Being with
you guys was so much fun.

01:11:52.137 --> 01:11:53.338 position:35% line:83% align:start
[CHIAKI]
I saw a river flow

01:11:53.372 --> 01:11:56.008 position:21% line:83% align:start
across the land for
the first time.

01:11:56.041 --> 01:12:00.012 position:30% line:83% align:start
I rode a bike
for the first time.

01:12:00.045 --> 01:12:04.350 position:19% line:83% align:start
I discovered just how
enormous the sky is.

01:12:04.384 --> 01:12:06.985 position:16% line:89% align:start
And more than anything,

01:12:07.019 --> 01:12:12.525 position:19% line:83% align:start
I'd never seen a place
with so many people.

01:12:12.559 --> 01:12:16.128 position:38% line:83% align:start
[MAKOTO]
Hey, Chiaki?

01:12:16.162 --> 01:12:19.097 position:13% line:83% align:start
I was wondering, is there
some kind of connection

01:12:19.132 --> 01:12:21.267 position:19% line:83% align:start
between that painting
and the future...

01:12:21.301 --> 01:12:23.470 position:5% line:89% align:start
...where you come from, I mean?

01:12:28.408 --> 01:12:33.146 position:13% line:89% align:start
Please, tell me. Is there?

01:12:35.315 --> 01:12:38.551 position:38% line:83% align:start
[CHIAKI]
I really like this era.

01:12:38.585 --> 01:12:39.686 position:24% line:89% align:start
You have baseball.

01:12:39.719 --> 01:12:42.755 position:13% line:83% align:start
Huh? Baseball disappears?
For real?

01:12:42.789 --> 01:12:44.324 position:24% line:89% align:start
Over here, stupid.

01:12:44.357 --> 01:12:49.429 position:38% line:83% align:start
[MAKOTO]
Huh?! Aww, stop messin' around.

01:12:49.462 --> 01:12:50.530 position:27% line:89% align:start
That painting...

01:12:50.563 --> 01:12:51.364 position:38% line:83% align:start
[CHIAKI]
Huh?

01:12:51.397 --> 01:12:53.700 position:21% line:83% align:start
--That painting...!
--[CHIAKI] Yeah?

01:12:53.734 --> 01:12:56.402 position:16% line:83% align:start
It's not there now, but
you'll be able to see it soon.

01:12:56.436 --> 01:12:59.072 position:19% line:83% align:start
It's getting restored.
That's why it's not there.

01:12:59.105 --> 01:13:02.141 position:7% line:83% align:start
How 'bout the three of us go?
You, me, and Kousuke?

01:13:02.175 --> 01:13:04.544 position:13% line:83% align:start
Especially now that summer
vacation's about to start!

01:13:04.578 --> 01:13:08.214 position:27% line:83% align:start
What do you say,
Chiaki? Chiaki?!

01:13:08.314 --> 01:13:10.450 position:27% line:89% align:start
Sorry, I can't.

01:13:10.483 --> 01:13:11.585 position:44% line:89% align:start
Uh?

01:13:11.619 --> 01:13:14.588 position:38% line:83% align:start
[CHIAKI]
As of tomorrow, I won't be here.

01:13:14.622 --> 01:13:16.790 position:38% line:83% align:start
[gasps]
How come?

01:13:16.824 --> 01:13:19.660 position:5% line:83% align:start
[CHIAKI] I'm not supposed to let
the people who live in the past

01:13:19.693 --> 01:13:22.128 position:19% line:89% align:start
know about time leaps.

01:13:22.161 --> 01:13:24.632 position:24% line:89% align:start
I broke that rule.

01:13:24.665 --> 01:13:26.634 position:30% line:89% align:start
That's why...

01:13:26.667 --> 01:13:28.802 position:24% line:83% align:start
...I won't be able
to see you again.

01:13:28.836 --> 01:13:33.274 position:16% line:83% align:start
I'll keep my mouth shut!
I promise I won't tell anyone!

01:13:33.307 --> 01:13:37.244 position:16% line:89% align:start
Chiaki! Where are you?!

01:13:37.278 --> 01:13:39.647 position:30% line:89% align:start
Hey, Chiaki...

01:13:39.680 --> 01:13:41.749 position:35% line:89% align:start
Chiaki...

01:13:41.782 --> 01:13:43.717 position:38% line:89% align:start
Chiaki!

01:13:43.751 --> 01:13:46.320 position:21% line:83% align:start
You said we'd go to
a night game together!

01:13:46.353 --> 01:13:47.354 position:38% line:83% align:start
[CHIAKI]
Sorry.

01:13:47.388 --> 01:13:50.591 position:16% line:83% align:start
And that we'd go to see
a fireworks festival!

01:13:50.624 --> 01:13:51.692 position:38% line:83% align:start
[CHIAKI]
I'm really sorry.

01:13:51.725 --> 01:13:55.796 position:16% line:83% align:start
So this means you don't
want to see me in a yukata?!

01:13:55.829 --> 01:13:59.667 position:16% line:83% align:start
[CHIAKI] Sorry, I would
liked to have seen that.

01:13:59.700 --> 01:14:01.235 position:41% line:89% align:start
Jerk!

01:14:06.574 --> 01:14:08.108 position:38% line:89% align:start
Chiaki!

01:14:09.844 --> 01:14:11.378 position:38% line:89% align:start
Chiaki!

01:14:17.384 --> 01:14:18.252 position:38% line:89% align:start
Chiaki!

01:14:18.285 --> 01:14:19.520 position:35% line:89% align:start
Uh! Wait!

01:14:19.553 --> 01:14:21.088 position:38% line:89% align:start
Chiaki!

01:14:48.215 --> 01:14:50.318 position:33% line:83% align:start
[STUDENT M]
Why is Chiaki quitting school?

01:14:50.352 --> 01:14:53.187 position:5% line:83% align:start
[STUDENT N] Apparently he was in
debt and the mob was after him.

01:14:53.220 --> 01:14:54.356 position:33% line:83% align:start
[STUDENT O]
Is that true?

01:14:54.389 --> 01:14:55.924 position:10% line:83% align:start
It's not something like his
parents getting a divorce?

01:14:55.957 --> 01:14:58.259 position:7% line:83% align:start
[STUDENT P] Well, I heard he's
marrying an older woman,

01:14:58.293 --> 01:14:59.661 position:10% line:89% align:start
because he got her pregnant.

01:14:59.694 --> 01:15:02.297 position:24% line:89% align:start
What?! Seriously!

01:15:02.330 --> 01:15:05.333 position:10% line:89% align:start
So what's the story, Makoto?

01:15:07.235 --> 01:15:08.903 position:27% line:83% align:start
I'm tellin' you,
he's not that kind of guy!

01:15:08.937 --> 01:15:11.539 position:19% line:83% align:start
I heard he lost it and
stabbed some guy.

01:15:11.573 --> 01:15:13.408 position:19% line:83% align:start
I heard he beat him up
with a baseball bat.

01:15:13.441 --> 01:15:15.377 position:13% line:83% align:start
[STUDENT Q] No. He took a
knife and stabbed him.

01:15:15.410 --> 01:15:18.346 position:7% line:89% align:start
I told you he's not like that!

01:15:18.380 --> 01:15:20.448 position:27% line:83% align:start
--Hey, Kousuke!
--Hey, c'mon. Come back!

01:15:20.482 --> 01:15:22.317 position:21% line:89% align:start
What's his problem?

01:15:28.390 --> 01:15:31.861 position:35% line:83% align:start
[KOUSUKE]
What the hell happened to him?

01:15:31.894 --> 01:15:33.361 position:27% line:89% align:start
[KOUSUKE sighs]

01:15:33.395 --> 01:15:36.197 position:35% line:83% align:start
[KOUSUKE]
It's one thing not to tell me,

01:15:36.231 --> 01:15:39.769 position:16% line:83% align:start
but he could've at least
talked to you about it.

01:15:39.802 --> 01:15:44.506 position:21% line:83% align:start
I mean, considering
he had a thing for you.

01:15:46.642 --> 01:15:48.476 position:38% line:83% align:start
[MAKOTO]
Did Chiaki say that?

01:15:48.510 --> 01:15:51.580 position:35% line:83% align:start
[KOUSUKE]
I thought it was obvious.

01:15:51.614 --> 01:15:53.816 position:24% line:89% align:start
Didn't you notice?

01:15:53.849 --> 01:15:57.720 position:21% line:83% align:start
Well, you're awkward
with stuff like that.

01:15:57.753 --> 01:16:04.325 position:19% line:83% align:start
M-Maybe that's why he
couldn't come out with it.

01:16:04.359 --> 01:16:05.594 position:38% line:83% align:start
[MAKOTO]
Kousuke...

01:16:05.628 --> 01:16:07.262 position:35% line:83% align:start
[KOUSUKE]
Yeah?

01:16:07.295 --> 01:16:08.664 position:38% line:83% align:start
[MAKOTO]
I'm a horrible person.

01:16:08.698 --> 01:16:10.700 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

01:16:10.733 --> 01:16:12.902 position:13% line:83% align:start
[MAKOTO] He wanted to tell
me something important,

01:16:12.935 --> 01:16:15.938 position:21% line:83% align:start
but I pretended the
conversation never happened.

01:16:15.971 --> 01:16:18.708 position:19% line:83% align:start
Why didn't I take what
he said more seriously?

01:16:18.741 --> 01:16:20.409 position:30% line:89% align:start
[MAKOTO sobs]

01:16:20.443 --> 01:16:24.814 position:27% line:83% align:start
Makoto, what are
you talkin' about?

01:16:24.847 --> 01:16:26.315 position:35% line:89% align:start
Uh! Wait!

01:16:26.348 --> 01:16:29.685 position:27% line:89% align:start
[MAKOTO panting]

01:16:29.785 --> 01:16:31.287 position:33% line:83% align:start
[STUDENT R]
Ah!

01:16:31.320 --> 01:16:40.629 position:35% line:89% align:start
[sobbing]

01:17:07.791 --> 01:17:10.927 position:38% line:83% align:start
[KAZUKO]
Feel any better?

01:17:10.961 --> 01:17:14.296 position:13% line:83% align:start
You know what, I honestly
thought you were just friends

01:17:14.330 --> 01:17:17.399 position:7% line:89% align:start
with both Kousuke and Chiaki.

01:17:23.039 --> 01:17:25.742 position:19% line:83% align:start
To tell you the truth,
I figured you would graduate

01:17:25.776 --> 01:17:27.444 position:30% line:83% align:start
without dating
either one of them,

01:17:27.477 --> 01:17:31.047 position:19% line:83% align:start
and you'd end up going
out with someone else entirely.

01:17:31.081 --> 01:17:34.551 position:19% line:83% align:start
[MAKOTO] That's what I
thought too, until yesterday.

01:17:34.584 --> 01:17:38.421 position:38% line:83% align:start
[KAZUKO]
But that's not how it is, right?

01:17:42.926 --> 01:17:47.564 position:10% line:83% align:start
I fell in love for the first
time when I was in senior high.

01:17:47.597 --> 01:17:49.833 position:21% line:83% align:start
We hit it off right
from the start.

01:17:49.866 --> 01:17:53.870 position:16% line:83% align:start
It was as if we'd known
each other all our lives.

01:17:53.904 --> 01:17:56.840 position:19% line:83% align:start
But it all fell apart
before we grew up.

01:17:59.910 --> 01:18:01.444 position:38% line:83% align:start
[MAKOTO]
Why?

01:18:02.479 --> 01:18:06.349 position:19% line:83% align:start
[KAZUKO] I don't know.
Bad timing, I guess.

01:18:06.383 --> 01:18:09.020 position:38% line:83% align:start
[MAKOTO]
What's he doing now?

01:18:10.121 --> 01:18:12.890 position:38% line:83% align:start
[KAZUKO]
I couldn't tell you.

01:18:12.924 --> 01:18:15.458 position:5% line:89% align:start
He promised to come back for me.

01:18:15.492 --> 01:18:18.029 position:21% line:83% align:start
I wasn't planning to
wait for him, but...

01:18:18.062 --> 01:18:21.999 position:19% line:83% align:start
Anyway, so many years
have passed now.

01:18:22.033 --> 01:18:27.905 position:13% line:83% align:start
It didn't seem very long.
Time flew by fast.

01:18:29.841 --> 01:18:31.042 position:38% line:83% align:start
[KAZUKO]
But, Makoto.

01:18:31.075 --> 01:18:32.176 position:38% line:83% align:start
[MAKOTO]
Hm?

01:18:32.210 --> 01:18:36.881 position:5% line:83% align:start
You're different. You're nothing
like me at all, are you?

01:18:41.052 --> 01:18:43.988 position:21% line:83% align:start
If a boy is late in
meeting up with you,

01:18:44.021 --> 01:18:47.058 position:27% line:83% align:start
you're the type
to go look for him.

01:18:50.695 --> 01:18:55.533 position:35% line:89% align:start
[slurping]

01:18:55.566 --> 01:18:57.501 position:21% line:89% align:start
Makoto, watermelon!

01:18:57.535 --> 01:18:58.936 position:30% line:83% align:start
[MAKOTO'S MOM]
Leave her, dear.

01:18:58.970 --> 01:18:59.904 position:30% line:83% align:start
[MAKOTO'S DAD]
What's up with her?

01:18:59.937 --> 01:19:02.473 position:10% line:83% align:start
Not coming down for dinner,
no watermelon?

01:19:02.506 --> 01:19:03.808 position:38% line:83% align:start
[MIYUKI]
She's heartbroken. That's what.

01:19:03.841 --> 01:19:04.876 position:27% line:89% align:start
You're kidding?!

01:19:04.909 --> 01:19:07.712 position:21% line:83% align:start
Miyuki, cut it out.
It's none of your business.

01:19:17.155 --> 01:19:20.024 position:13% line:83% align:start
[MIYUKI] If a boy is late
in meeting up with you,

01:19:20.057 --> 01:19:22.994 position:27% line:83% align:start
you're the type
to go look for him.

01:19:33.005 --> 01:19:36.741 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

01:19:36.774 --> 01:19:39.211 position:38% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

01:19:39.244 --> 01:19:41.046 position:38% line:89% align:start
[groans]

01:19:41.079 --> 01:19:43.148 position:38% line:89% align:start
No way!

01:19:43.181 --> 01:19:45.650 position:21% line:89% align:start
It was zero before.

01:19:49.821 --> 01:19:51.924 position:27% line:89% align:start
It can't be...!

01:19:51.957 --> 01:19:53.859 position:27% line:89% align:start
[MAKOTO panting]

01:19:53.892 --> 01:19:55.626 position:16% line:83% align:start
--[MAKOTO'S MOM] Makoto!
--[MIYUKI] Sis!

01:19:55.661 --> 01:19:57.595 position:30% line:83% align:start
[MAKOTO'S DAD]
Hey, take it easy, Makoto!

01:19:59.798 --> 01:20:00.999 position:30% line:83% align:start
[MAKOTO'S DAD]
Makoto!

01:20:01.033 --> 01:20:04.036 position:35% line:89% align:start
[panting]

01:20:04.069 --> 01:20:06.538 position:10% line:83% align:start
[MAKOTO] Chiaki time leaped
in order to save Kousuke.

01:20:06.571 --> 01:20:07.739 position:13% line:89% align:start
So I got my last one back.

01:20:07.773 --> 01:20:10.642 position:10% line:83% align:start
If I can go back far enough,
he should get his back, too!

01:20:10.676 --> 01:20:12.477 position:33% line:89% align:start
Oh, Makoto!

01:20:12.511 --> 01:20:14.079 position:38% line:83% align:start
[MAKOTO]
I'm almost positive.

01:20:22.187 --> 01:20:25.190 position:35% line:89% align:start
[screams]

01:20:53.919 --> 01:20:56.289 position:24% line:83% align:start
[FUKUSHIMA-SENSEI]
Setlle down, kids.

01:20:56.322 --> 01:20:58.724 position:24% line:89% align:start
Huh? Who are you?

01:20:58.757 --> 01:21:01.260 position:10% line:83% align:start
[KOUSUKE] I'm Kousuke Tsuda,
and this Makoto Konno.

01:21:01.294 --> 01:21:02.195 position:38% line:83% align:start
[CHIAKI]
Konno?

01:21:02.228 --> 01:21:03.528 position:24% line:83% align:start
[FUKUSHIMA-SENSEI]
He looks a bit rough,

01:21:03.562 --> 01:21:04.897 position:7% line:89% align:start
but I hope you all get along.

01:21:04.931 --> 01:21:07.133 position:35% line:83% align:start
[KOUSUKE]
Makoto, over here!

01:21:07.166 --> 01:21:09.601 position:38% line:83% align:start
[CHIAKI]
See ya, Makoto!

01:21:09.634 --> 01:21:11.670 position:35% line:83% align:start
[KOUSUKE]
Hey, did you hear that?

01:21:11.703 --> 01:21:13.873 position:24% line:83% align:start
He called you by
your first name.

01:21:24.083 --> 01:21:28.821 position:16% line:83% align:start
[CHIAKI] Makoto, what do
you say? Wanna go out?

01:21:28.855 --> 01:21:29.989 position:24% line:83% align:start
You were wondering
what it'd be like

01:21:30.023 --> 01:21:32.025 position:10% line:89% align:start
if Kousuke got a girlfriend.

01:21:32.058 --> 01:21:35.695 position:7% line:89% align:start
I mean... I'm not ugly, am I?

01:21:54.647 --> 01:21:58.985 position:24% line:89% align:start
[MAKOTO groaning]

01:21:59.018 --> 01:22:00.053 position:44% line:89% align:start
Ah!

01:22:00.086 --> 01:22:03.157 position:38% line:89% align:start
[groans]

01:22:10.963 --> 01:22:12.299 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

01:22:18.205 --> 01:22:19.973 position:41% line:83% align:start
[YURI]
Makoto?

01:22:21.874 --> 01:22:23.243 position:30% line:89% align:start
Are you okay?

01:22:27.314 --> 01:22:30.683 position:10% line:83% align:start
[YURI] I wonder what Chiaki
does on the weekends and stuff.

01:22:30.716 --> 01:22:34.654 position:16% line:83% align:start
I'm sure he doesn't play
baseball all the time.

01:22:38.392 --> 01:22:39.860 position:38% line:83% align:start
[MAKOTO]
Yuri...

01:22:39.893 --> 01:22:41.095 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

01:22:41.128 --> 01:22:45.099 position:13% line:83% align:start
[MAKOTO] There's something
I haven't been able to tell you.

01:22:45.132 --> 01:22:47.801 position:41% line:83% align:start
[YURI]
Yeah? What is it?

01:22:47.835 --> 01:22:50.804 position:5% line:89% align:start
It's Chiaki. I really like him.

01:22:50.838 --> 01:22:52.172 position:41% line:89% align:start
A lot.

01:22:54.241 --> 01:22:56.844 position:35% line:89% align:start
I'm sorry.

01:23:00.314 --> 01:23:04.384 position:13% line:89% align:start
I see. I kinda thought so.

01:23:04.419 --> 01:23:09.723 position:7% line:83% align:start
I bumped into Chiaki on my way
here. You should go to him.

01:23:09.756 --> 01:23:11.091 position:38% line:83% align:start
[MAKOTO]
Mm.

01:23:15.330 --> 01:23:18.031 position:38% line:89% align:start
Makoto.

01:23:18.065 --> 01:23:20.033 position:16% line:89% align:start
Time waits for no one...

01:23:21.168 --> 01:23:24.405 position:35% line:83% align:start
[KOUSUKE]
Makoto!

01:23:24.439 --> 01:23:27.107 position:38% line:83% align:start
[MAKOTO]
Kousuke, where's Chiaki?

01:23:27.142 --> 01:23:28.243 position:35% line:83% align:start
[KOUSUKE]
He got tired of waiting

01:23:28.276 --> 01:23:29.977 position:10% line:89% align:start
and went ahead to the field.

01:23:30.010 --> 01:23:32.913 position:21% line:83% align:start
He's pretty cranky.
We'd better hurry.

01:23:32.946 --> 01:23:35.183 position:16% line:83% align:start
You sure you wanna leave
your girlfriend alone?

01:23:35.216 --> 01:23:36.217 position:24% line:89% align:start
After all I did--

01:23:36.251 --> 01:23:37.918 position:7% line:89% align:start
What do you mean "girlfriend"?

01:23:37.951 --> 01:23:40.787 position:21% line:83% align:start
Oh, right. It's all
gone back to before...

01:23:40.821 --> 01:23:42.756 position:21% line:83% align:start
What're you mumbling
to yourself about?

01:23:42.789 --> 01:23:44.725 position:33% line:89% align:start
Uh, nothing!

01:23:44.758 --> 01:23:47.028 position:41% line:83% align:start
--Uh?
--Hm?

01:23:48.363 --> 01:23:52.000 position:7% line:89% align:start
[MORIKO, SEKIMI gasp, chatter]

01:23:52.033 --> 01:23:53.368 position:38% line:83% align:start
[MAKOTO]
Hey, why don't we invite them

01:23:53.401 --> 01:23:54.469 position:19% line:89% align:start
to play ball with us?

01:23:54.502 --> 01:23:55.370 position:24% line:89% align:start
What? You serious?

01:23:55.403 --> 01:23:56.737 position:38% line:83% align:start
[MAKOTO]
Go and ask them.

01:23:56.771 --> 01:23:57.605 position:21% line:89% align:start
Yeah? Why should I?

01:23:57.639 --> 01:24:00.775 position:38% line:83% align:start
[MAKOTO]
The more, the merrier, right?

01:24:00.808 --> 01:24:04.145 position:13% line:83% align:start
Yeah, sure, but, come on,
do you even know 'em?

01:24:04.179 --> 01:24:06.714 position:5% line:89% align:start
Kind of. Hey! That reminds me...

01:24:06.748 --> 01:24:07.749 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

01:24:07.782 --> 01:24:09.918 position:21% line:83% align:start
Borrow my bike, and
it'll cost you 5,000 yen.

01:24:09.951 --> 01:24:10.985 position:41% line:89% align:start
What?!

01:24:11.019 --> 01:24:13.188 position:38% line:83% align:start
[MAKOTO]
Got that? 5,000 yen!

01:24:13.221 --> 01:24:15.156 position:21% line:83% align:start
Hang on! What's this
all about anyway?

01:24:15.190 --> 01:24:17.859 position:10% line:83% align:start
Ask them nicely, "Would you
like to play ball with us?"

01:24:17.892 --> 01:24:20.228 position:35% line:89% align:start
Like that.

01:24:20.261 --> 01:24:22.130 position:13% line:83% align:start
--[MAKOTO] One more thing!
--[KOUSUKE] Huh?

01:24:22.163 --> 01:24:24.299 position:38% line:83% align:start
[MAKOTO]
Thanks for waiting for me!

01:24:26.901 --> 01:24:27.802 position:33% line:89% align:start
Hey, Makoto!

01:24:27.835 --> 01:24:28.671 position:38% line:83% align:start
[MAKOTO]
What?!

01:24:28.703 --> 01:24:31.773 position:35% line:83% align:start
[KOUSUKE]
Watch where you're goin'!

01:24:31.806 --> 01:24:33.141 position:38% line:83% align:start
[MAKOTO]
Sure!

01:24:41.849 --> 01:24:47.456 position:35% line:89% align:start
[panting]

01:25:09.945 --> 01:25:14.216 position:21% line:89% align:start
[panting continues]

01:25:46.882 --> 01:25:52.821 position:30% line:89% align:start
[MAKOTO pants]

01:25:53.355 --> 01:25:55.958 position:38% line:83% align:start
[CHIAKI]
You're late. Where's Kousuke?

01:25:55.991 --> 01:25:57.993 position:19% line:83% align:start
--[MAKOTO] Not coming.
--[CHIAKI] Huh?

01:25:58.027 --> 01:26:00.363 position:27% line:83% align:start
What do you mean
he's not coming?

01:26:03.866 --> 01:26:05.868 position:38% line:83% align:start
[CHIAKI]
Uh?!

01:26:08.538 --> 01:26:11.040 position:38% line:83% align:start
[CHIAKI]
Uh... Where'd you find that?

01:26:11.073 --> 01:26:14.043 position:16% line:83% align:start
I-I mean, d-do you even
know what it is?

01:26:14.076 --> 01:26:16.246 position:16% line:89% align:start
Yeah, I know what it is.

01:26:16.279 --> 01:26:17.880 position:38% line:83% align:start
[CHIAKI]
Wha... Who told you?

01:26:17.913 --> 01:26:19.048 position:38% line:89% align:start
You did.

01:26:19.082 --> 01:26:22.851 position:10% line:83% align:start
Give me a break. I did not.
I never told you about it.

01:26:22.885 --> 01:26:24.953 position:24% line:83% align:start
Actually, you told
me everything.

01:26:24.987 --> 01:26:27.490 position:16% line:83% align:start
About how you came here
from the future,

01:26:27.524 --> 01:26:29.459 position:10% line:89% align:start
and what this thing does...

01:26:29.492 --> 01:26:31.127 position:33% line:89% align:start
Everything.

01:26:31.161 --> 01:26:33.363 position:35% line:89% align:start
Uh... Uh!

01:26:33.396 --> 01:26:35.332 position:38% line:83% align:start
[MAKOTO]
I thought so.

01:26:35.365 --> 01:26:37.167 position:27% line:89% align:start
Thank goodness.

01:26:37.200 --> 01:26:39.402 position:38% line:83% align:start
[CHIAKI]
Where did you come from?

01:26:39.436 --> 01:26:41.004 position:16% line:89% align:start
I came from the future.

01:26:41.037 --> 01:26:41.905 position:38% line:83% align:start
[CHIAKI]
Can you time leap?

01:26:41.938 --> 01:26:43.540 position:13% line:89% align:start
I could, but not anymore.

01:26:43.573 --> 01:26:45.375 position:16% line:83% align:start
[CHIAKI] Did I actually
tell you all that?

01:26:45.408 --> 01:26:46.409 position:44% line:89% align:start
Yup.

01:26:46.443 --> 01:26:48.111 position:21% line:89% align:start
And you believed me?

01:26:48.144 --> 01:26:49.045 position:41% line:89% align:start
Mm-hm.

01:26:49.079 --> 01:26:50.880 position:13% line:83% align:start
--[CHIAKI] What an idiot!
--Yeah, maybe.

01:26:50.914 --> 01:26:53.083 position:7% line:83% align:start
[CHIAKI] So, you came all the
way back to tell me that?

01:26:53.116 --> 01:26:54.451 position:41% line:89% align:start
Yeah.

01:26:56.186 --> 01:26:57.320 position:27% line:89% align:start
[CHIAKI groans]

01:27:00.390 --> 01:27:04.595 position:7% line:83% align:start
[CHIAKI] Why would I tell you?
How could I be so stupid?

01:27:53.344 --> 01:27:58.582 position:5% line:83% align:start
[MAKOTO] When you go back to the
future, enjoy that painting.

01:27:58.616 --> 01:28:02.119 position:30% line:83% align:start
It's not gonna
get lost or burned.

01:28:02.153 --> 01:28:03.621 position:24% line:83% align:start
I'll figure out a
way to make sure

01:28:03.654 --> 01:28:06.056 position:7% line:89% align:start
it's preserved for the future.

01:28:09.326 --> 01:28:13.264 position:38% line:83% align:start
[CHIAKI]
Thanks. I'd appreciate that.

01:28:15.566 --> 01:28:18.269 position:13% line:83% align:start
I was supposed to go back
right after I got here,

01:28:18.302 --> 01:28:21.539 position:21% line:83% align:start
but all of a sudden,
it was summer.

01:28:21.572 --> 01:28:28.179 position:16% line:83% align:start
Time sorta just flew by,
'cause you guys are so much fun.

01:28:28.212 --> 01:28:31.248 position:27% line:83% align:start
Yeah, but that's
not all you said.

01:28:31.282 --> 01:28:33.317 position:38% line:83% align:start
[CHIAKI]
Then what did I say?

01:28:42.259 --> 01:28:44.329 position:33% line:89% align:start
Not telling.

01:28:44.362 --> 01:28:46.731 position:27% line:89% align:start
C'mon. Why not?

01:28:46.765 --> 01:28:50.134 position:19% line:83% align:start
I'm serious. You gotta
tell me what I said.

01:28:50.167 --> 01:28:51.269 position:38% line:83% align:start
[MAKOTO]
I'm not telling.

01:28:51.303 --> 01:28:55.707 position:5% line:83% align:start
You have to tell me. Don't leave
me in the dark. Come on!

01:28:55.740 --> 01:28:57.642 position:38% line:83% align:start
[BOY A]
Aw, look at the lovers.

01:28:57.676 --> 01:28:58.075 position:27% line:83% align:start
[MAKOTO, CHIAKI]
Uh?!

01:28:58.108 --> 01:28:59.611 position:27% line:89% align:start
You're in love!

01:28:59.644 --> 01:29:02.180 position:27% line:89% align:start
Mm. I love you!

01:29:02.214 --> 01:29:03.348 position:41% line:89% align:start
Kiss!

01:29:03.381 --> 01:29:05.450 position:38% line:83% align:start
[CHIAKI]
Hey, hey! Get lost, rugrats!

01:29:05.484 --> 01:29:07.552 position:16% line:83% align:start
--Let's get out of here!
--Hurry!

01:29:07.586 --> 01:29:09.120 position:33% line:89% align:start
Wait for me!

01:29:10.822 --> 01:29:12.357 position:30% line:89% align:start
[CHIAKI sighs]

01:29:20.332 --> 01:29:23.068 position:38% line:83% align:start
[CHIAKI]
Say "bye" to Kousuke for me.

01:29:23.101 --> 01:29:25.303 position:13% line:83% align:start
Tell him sorry I couldn't
say goodbye in person.

01:29:25.337 --> 01:29:28.106 position:38% line:83% align:start
[MAKOTO]
Sure.

01:29:28.139 --> 01:29:31.243 position:38% line:83% align:start
[CHIAKI]
Oh, um, ah, o-one more thing.

01:29:36.749 --> 01:29:38.684 position:38% line:83% align:start
[MAKOTO]
Yeah?

01:29:38.718 --> 01:29:40.585 position:13% line:83% align:start
[CHIAKI] There's something
I've been meaning to tell you

01:29:40.619 --> 01:29:42.655 position:21% line:89% align:start
for a long time now.

01:29:46.558 --> 01:29:48.093 position:38% line:83% align:start
[CHIAKI]
Listen...

01:29:51.196 --> 01:29:52.364 position:7% line:89% align:start
Don't go gettin' yourself hurt

01:29:52.397 --> 01:29:56.502 position:16% line:83% align:start
by jumping out in front
of things, okay?

01:29:56.536 --> 01:29:57.837 position:38% line:83% align:start
[MAKOTO]
Aw...

01:29:57.870 --> 01:30:00.338 position:19% line:83% align:start
[CHIAKI] I'm serious.
You need to be more careful.

01:30:00.372 --> 01:30:05.411 position:5% line:83% align:start
The ol' "look be fore you leap"
thing definitely works.

01:30:05.444 --> 01:30:07.078 position:30% line:89% align:start
Unbelievable.

01:30:07.112 --> 01:30:09.448 position:19% line:83% align:start
That's the last thing
you have to say to me?

01:30:09.482 --> 01:30:12.285 position:38% line:83% align:start
[CHIAKI]
I'm looking out for ya, stupid.

01:30:16.355 --> 01:30:19.525 position:7% line:83% align:start
Fine, then! Thank you so much
for looking out for me!

01:30:19.559 --> 01:30:21.360 position:19% line:89% align:start
Now, hurry up and go!

01:30:21.394 --> 01:30:23.329 position:38% line:83% align:start
[CHIAKI]
What are you upset about?!

01:30:23.362 --> 01:30:25.231 position:38% line:83% align:start
[MAKOTO]
Just go!

01:30:26.666 --> 01:30:27.500 position:38% line:83% align:start
[CHIAKI]
See ya.

01:30:27.533 --> 01:30:30.102 position:30% line:89% align:start
Yeah, see ya!

01:30:41.614 --> 01:30:44.850 position:24% line:89% align:start
[COUPLE laughing]

01:30:49.355 --> 01:30:51.090 position:38% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

01:30:56.462 --> 01:31:02.168 position:35% line:89% align:start
[sobbing]

01:31:04.905 --> 01:31:07.774 position:27% line:89% align:start
I don't get it.

01:31:07.808 --> 01:31:14.848 position:35% line:89% align:start
[wailing]

01:31:27.594 --> 01:31:31.465 position:35% line:89% align:start
[sobbing]

01:31:42.309 --> 01:31:44.845 position:16% line:89% align:start
I'll be waiting for you.

01:31:49.783 --> 01:31:54.621 position:19% line:83% align:start
'Kay. I won't be long.
I'll come running.

01:32:26.253 --> 01:32:27.587 position:35% line:83% align:start
[KOUSUKE]
Makoto...

01:32:29.791 --> 01:32:31.324 position:35% line:83% align:start
[KOUSUKE]
Makoto...!

01:32:32.559 --> 01:32:35.395 position:35% line:83% align:start
[KOUSUKE]
Hey, Makoto!

01:32:46.641 --> 01:32:48.776 position:5% line:89% align:start
Incredible. I don't believe it.

01:32:48.810 --> 01:32:51.846 position:7% line:83% align:start
Me, I could understand, but to
leave without sayin' bye to you?

01:32:51.879 --> 01:32:53.681 position:21% line:83% align:start
And all of a sudden
he's leavin' school

01:32:53.715 --> 01:32:56.651 position:5% line:89% align:start
'cause he's gonna study abroad.

01:32:56.684 --> 01:32:58.619 position:13% line:89% align:start
Aw, c'mon. Gimme a break!

01:32:58.653 --> 01:32:59.987 position:41% line:83% align:start
[KAHO]
Oh! Sorry!

01:33:04.325 --> 01:33:06.427 position:38% line:83% align:start
[MAKOTO]
Don't worry about it.

01:33:06.461 --> 01:33:09.630 position:16% line:83% align:start
He probably figured out
what he wanted to do.

01:33:09.664 --> 01:33:12.467 position:35% line:83% align:start
[KOUSUKE]
Wait. Did he tell you somethin'?

01:33:12.500 --> 01:33:15.837 position:7% line:89% align:start
Tell me something? Like what?

01:33:15.870 --> 01:33:18.840 position:27% line:83% align:start
--[KAHO grunts]
--[MORIKO, SEKIMI groan]

01:33:18.873 --> 01:33:20.341 position:41% line:83% align:start
[KAHO]
S-Sorry!

01:33:20.374 --> 01:33:21.876 position:30% line:83% align:start
[MORIKO] Kaho,
you throw like a girl.

01:33:21.909 --> 01:33:23.011 position:30% line:89% align:start
Look at her...

01:33:23.045 --> 01:33:26.581 position:7% line:83% align:start
[MAKOTO] I've made a decision
about my future, too.

01:33:26.614 --> 01:33:28.850 position:35% line:89% align:start
Oh? What?

01:33:28.883 --> 01:33:30.718 position:38% line:83% align:start
[MAKOTO]
It's a secret!

01:33:30.752 --> 01:33:34.589 position:27% line:83% align:start
How come? What?
Don't you trust me?

01:33:34.622 --> 01:33:37.391 position:16% line:89% align:start
Tell ya some other time.

01:34:12.027 --> 01:34:14.463 position:38% line:83% align:start
[SEKIMI]
Makoto, hey!

01:34:14.496 --> 01:34:16.297 position:38% line:83% align:start
[MAKOTO]
Ready!

01:34:21.136 --> 01:34:22.838 position:38% line:83% align:start
[MAKOTO]
Good throw!

01:34:24.373 --> 01:34:26.542 position:30% line:89% align:start
Here it comes!

